{"id":389,"date":"2022-05-22T16:35:51","date_gmt":"2022-05-22T16:35:51","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/soncovax.com\/?p=389"},"modified":"2024-11-17T09:56:31","modified_gmt":"2024-11-17T09:56:31","slug":"nhung-mau-son-nha-duoc-ua-chuong-nhat-hien-nay","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/nhung-mau-son-nha-duoc-ua-chuong-nhat-hien-nay\/","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u01a1n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p th\u00ec c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u01a1n nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o thu h\u00fat m\u1ecdi \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn. M\u00e0u s\u01a1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb9p, c\u00f3 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a m\u1edbi to\u00e1t l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p, s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n nh\u00e0. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u00e0u s\u01a1n hi\u1ec7n nay r\u1ea5t \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn theo \u00fd th\u00edch, phong c\u00e1ch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i<b><i>\u00a0<\/i><\/b>s\u1ebd g\u1ee3i \u00fd nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n tham kh\u1ea3o khi b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o m\u1edbi cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\r\n<h2 id=\"1-mau-trang-luon-khang-dinh-the-thuong-phong\">1. M\u00e0u tr\u1eafng lu\u00f4n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1ee3ng phong<\/h2>\r\n<p>M\u00e0u tr\u1eafng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u00e0u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u gia ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u01a1n nh\u00e0, b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u00e0u hay c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1eadt kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u1ed7i m\u1ed1t, m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng c\u00f2n gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng, s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u1ecf.<\/p>\r\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1734430535\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"366\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/ma-trang.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1734430535 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\r\n<h2 id=\"2-mau-xam-sang-trong-va-dang-cap\">2. M\u00e0u x\u00e1m sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p<\/h2>\r\n<p>Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u01a1n trung t\u00ednh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c gia ch\u1ee7, m\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u01a1n ghi x\u00e1m l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111en, tr\u1eafng, c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd to\u00e1t l\u00ean v\u1ebb th\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong ch\u1edbp m\u1eaft. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng th\u00eam t\u00ednh tr\u1ebb trung, \u0111\u1eebng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 trang tr\u00ed m\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt kh\u00e1c b\u1edfi m\u00e0u x\u00e1m lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 b\u1ee9c n\u1ec1n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho m\u1ecdi m\u00e0u s\u1eafc kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\r\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1549958037\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"496\" height=\"350\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/mau-xam.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1549958037 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\r\n<h2 id=\"3-mau-vang-nang-dong\">3. M\u00e0u v\u00e0ng n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/h2>\r\n<p>L\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u01a1n mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u01a1i, m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ebb tr\u1ebb trung, n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu th\u00eam v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n<p>M\u00e0u v\u00e0ng s\u00e1ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan, t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u0103n nh\u00e0. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng kem l\u1ea1i mang ch\u00fat h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n, ho\u00e0i ni\u1ec7m, m\u1ed9c m\u1ea1c, t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, th\u01b0 th\u00e1i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u0103n nh\u00e0. M\u00e0u v\u00e0ng cam, v\u00e0ng n\u00e2u l\u00e0 gam m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng.<\/p>\r\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1098204393\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/mau-vang.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1098204393 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\r\n<h2 id=\"4-mau-den-quyen-luc\">4. M\u00e0u \u0111en quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c<\/h2>\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, ph\u00e1 b\u1ecf m\u1ecdi gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a m\u00e0u \u0111en ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn n\u00f3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. M\u00e0u \u0111en l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eadm,\u00a0ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng \u0111\u1eb9p.<\/p>\r\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1075945763\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"483\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/mau-den.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/mau-den.jpg 700w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/mau-den-600x414.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1075945763 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\r\n<h2 id=\"5-mau-xanh-mang-ve-dep-cua-dai-duong\">5. M\u00e0u xanh mang v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/h2>\r\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u c\u1ef1c k\u00ec l\u1ea1 m\u1eaft, n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi xanh bi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 xanh l\u00e1 c\u00e2y. N\u00f3 mang m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n m\u00e0 ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tone m\u00e0u l\u1ea1nh n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u00e0y trong kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1edfi n\u00f3 v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, v\u1eeba hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u cho kh\u00f4ng gian.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1452225799\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/mau-xanh.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1452225799 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\r\n<h2 id=\"6-mau-tim-nhat-lang-man-va-tinh-te\">6. M\u00e0u t\u00edm nh\u1ea1t l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf<\/h2>\r\n<p>M\u00e0u t\u00edm v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 cao c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng. Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u00e0 s\u01a1n m\u00e0u n\u00e0y, s\u1ebd g\u1ee3i l\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac t\u1eeb ni\u1ec1m vui \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng, \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<\/p>\r\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1602961665\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/mau-tim.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1602961665 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p th\u00ec c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u01a1n nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 